    <h3 class="title">Notes</h3>
			
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_020"><a name="-04205_000_020">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote1-04205_000_020">1.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Robert&nbsp;D. Hales, &ldquo;A Gospel Vision of Welfare: Faith in Action,&rdquo; in <span class="emphasis">Basic Principles of Welfare and Self-Reliance </span>(booklet, 2009), 1.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_020"><a name="-04205_000_020">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
